<HEADLINE>
`TAKE TWO PILLS AND CLICK ME IN THE MORNING'  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent 525-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 8 August 1998) Economist magazine.)  
  
