heard the voice of the young woman whose appearance at a federal
courthouse Thursday morning drew a dozen satellite trucks and
scores of reporters who mostly wound up interviewing each other
about their brief glimpse of her. But Monica Lewinsky has plenty to
say, according to several people she has spent time with since the
