Tomjanovich is none of these things. By Bob Ryan.
</P>
<P>
   TV-SPORTS-COLUMN (New York) -- Armen Keteyian's selection by CBS
for its top NFL broadcast team signals a transformation in the job
usually limited to trivia. By Howard Manly.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
