<P>
   CATALOG-SHOPPING (Undated) Lots about the fast-growing trend of
catalog shopping, from Amy Blankenship, director of the Direct
Marketing Association's shop-at-home information center. Also, how
catalogs are going to compete with online shopping _ by going
online themselves. mug and catalog scan.
