a pixie-face boy called Peter Pan? Well, he's making a return
flight to Southern California for a brief stay. The young boy who
vowed he would never grow up soars on to the local stage in a new
national touring production, starring Cathy Rigby as ``Peter Pan.''
By Nancy Hewitt. 
