DORMS-DESIGN (Los Angeles) _ The summer's winding down and those
thick envelopes have arrived in the mail _ dorm room assignments.
Back to those drab little boxes with a couple of twin beds and worn
out furniture. But it doesn't have to look like that. Local
designers and merchants pitch in to show us how to liven up a plain
dorm room as you _ or your kids _ head back to college. By Jenifer
Hanrahan. 
. 
