<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    NEWS ANALYSIS: WHY DOES AMERICA HAVE TERRORIST ENEMIES?
 &HT;    With BOMBING-CLINTON-0808.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
