<P>
   AFRICA-BOMBINGS (Nairobi, Kenya) _ Ledeall: Two massive bombs
devastated the U.S. embassies in Kenya and Tanzania on Friday
morning, killing several American officials and more than 80 other
people, in what appeared to be simultaneous terrorist attacks. By
