<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-07 19:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3775 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FUNDS-WATCH-ART-$ADV0     08-07 0768
