<P>
   BKO-TEAM-USA (Athens) _ Team USA plays Italy in the World
Basketball Championships. The loser of the game is game in
eliminated from medal contention. By EDDIE SEFKO.
</P>
<P>
   With: BKO-BLINEBURY-COLUMN
</P>
<P>
   BBN-ASTROS (Houston) _ The Houston Astros and Philadelphia
Phillies play in Randy Johnson's Astrodome debut before what could
be the biggest baseball crowd in Astrodome history. By JOSEPH
DUARTE.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-CROWD (Houston) _ Sidebar on fans flocking to Randy
Johnson's debut. By JEROME SOLOMON.
</P>
<P>
   With: BBN-ROBERTSON-COLUMN
</P>
<P>
   For Sunday:
