His approach to pottery has brought him a large fan club,
especially among the fashion designers he admires. ``I rarely go in
someone's house who doesn't have his work somewhere,'' says men's
wear designer Gene Meyer, who has several of his pieces. (Angel
Franco/New York Times Photo)
